The paper discusses the characteristics and limitations of funding acknowledgement data in Web of Science, which is a bibliographic database commonly used in the fields of computer science, digital libraries, information retrieval, cybersecurity, and security and privacy. Therefore, the most likely arXiv CS sub-category for this paper is cs.DL (Digital Libraries), followed by cs.IR (Information Retrieval), cs.CY (Cybersecurity), cs.CR (Security and Privacy), and cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
